WEBVTT

00:03.015 --> 00:05.006
AND EVERYTHING NICE.

00:05.008 --> 00:08.018
THESE WERE THE INGREDIENTS
CHOSEN TO CREATE THE
PERFECT LITTLE GIRL.

00:08.020 --> 00:14.019
BUT PROFESSOR UTONIUM
ACCIDENTALLY ADDED AN EXTRA
INGREDIENT TO THE CONCOCTION--

00:14.021 --> 00:15.025
CHEMICAL X.

00:15.027 --> 00:18.025
[EXPLOSION]

00:18.027 --> 00:21.015
THUS THE POWERPUFF GIRLS
WERE BORN!

00:21.017 --> 00:22.026
USING THEIR ULTRA-SUPERPOWERS,

00:22.028 --> 00:26.029
BLOSSOM, BUBBLES, AND BUTTERCUP
HAVE DEDICATED THEIR LIVES

00:27.001 --> 00:31.012
TO FIGHTING CRIME
AND THE FORCES OF EVIL!

00:59.008 --> 01:04.004
CAPTIONING MADE POSSIBLE BY
TURNER ENTERTAINMENT GROUP
AND U.S. DEPARTMENT OF EDUCATION

01:13.022 --> 01:18.021
THE CITY OF TOWNSVILLE
ON THE PLANET EARTH
OUT IN OUTER SPACE.

01:18.023 --> 01:21.016
AND NOT TOO FAR OUT
IN OUTER SPACE,

01:21.018 --> 01:23.005
JUST BEHIND THE EARTH'S MOON,

01:23.007 --> 01:26.014
A MYSTERIOUS CRAFT LIES IN WAIT.

01:26.016 --> 01:28.003
Alien:
TARGET ACHIEVED,
YOUR HIGHNESS.

01:28.005 --> 01:31.001
FIRING SEQUENCE READY
ON YOUR COMMAND.

01:31.003 --> 01:35.012
Second alien: EXCELLENT.
LAUNCH THE STORPEDO.

01:51.024 --> 01:54.006
Narrator:
THE TOWN OF FARMSVILLE,

01:54.008 --> 01:56.022
A QUIET, HARDWORKING
AGRICULTURAL COMMUNITY,

01:56.024 --> 02:00.026
WHOSE RESIDENTS
TAKE HUMBLE PRIDE IN
THE MOST IMPORTANT OF DUTIES--

02:00.028 --> 02:03.001
THE GROWING OF
WHOLESOME, NATURAL FOODS

02:03.003 --> 02:05.000
WHICH ARE PROMPTLY HARVESTED,

02:05.002 --> 02:10.002
PACKED, AND SHIPPED TO
THE MANY HUNGRY AND GRATEFUL
RESIDENTS OF TOWNSVILLE.

02:10.004 --> 02:14.018
THESE BUSY CITY DWELLERS MAY
HAVE IMPORTANT APPOINTMENTS
TO KEEP,

02:14.020 --> 02:15.013
DEALS TO MAKE,

02:15.015 --> 02:16.017
INFORMATION TO DISTRIBUTE,

02:16.019 --> 02:18.006
AND CONSTRUCTIONS TO CONSTRUCT,

02:18.008 --> 02:22.000
BUT NONE OF THE BUSINESS
THAT IS TOWNSVILLE
COULD EVEN BEGIN

02:22.002 --> 02:23.028
WITHOUT A TRIP TO THE MARKET

02:24.000 --> 02:29.018
AND A HEAPING PLATE FULL OF
THAT NUTRITIOUS, DELICIOUS
FARM-RAISED GOODNESS.

02:29.020 --> 02:31.005
MM-MMM.

02:31.007 --> 02:32.000
COME ON, KIDS.

02:32.002 --> 02:33.022
EAT YOUR
VEGETABLES.

02:33.024 --> 02:35.007
NO WAY, JOSE.

02:35.009 --> 02:36.017
YEAH.
NO WAY, JOSE.

02:36.019 --> 02:38.019
I DON'T EAT
BROCCOLI.

02:38.021 --> 02:42.002
YEAH. I DON'T EAT
BLOCLORI.

02:42.004 --> 02:44.022
HERE COMES THE BROCCOLI EXPRESS!

02:44.024 --> 02:47.005
WOO-WOO. INTO THE TUNNEL.

02:47.007 --> 02:51.027
HERE COMES THE PIRATE SHIP
TO HIDE TREASURE IN
THE SECRET CAVE!

02:51.029 --> 02:56.000
HERE COMES THE X-WING SPACE
FIGHTER ZOOMING AROUND
THROUGH HYPERSPACE

02:56.002 --> 03:00.023
WITH PROTON TORPEDOS
TO BLOW UP THE DEATH STAR!

03:01.019 --> 03:03.010
YUCK! I AIN'T
EATIN' THAT!

03:03.012 --> 03:04.028
WHY?

03:05.000 --> 03:06.025
BECAUSE VEGETABLES
IS FOR SISSIES AND
RABBITS, RIGHT, DAD?

03:06.027 --> 03:08.006
RIGHT.

03:08.008 --> 03:09.024
AND EATIN'
THE FLESH OF
STUPID LESSER BEASTS

03:09.026 --> 03:12.007
MAKES YOU STRONG,
RIGHT, DAD?

03:12.009 --> 03:13.025
RIGHT.

03:18.021 --> 03:23.017
EEW. WHAT'S THAT
ICKY GREEN STUFF?

03:23.019 --> 03:26.008
IT DEFINITELY
ISN'T CAKE.

03:26.010 --> 03:27.026
IT AIN'T
A CORN DOG.

03:27.028 --> 03:30.003
I KNOW IT'S
NOT A HAMSTER.

03:30.005 --> 03:31.018
YOU EAT HAMSTERS?

03:31.020 --> 03:33.018
NO! I LIKE HAMSTERS,

03:33.020 --> 03:37.000
AND I KNOW I DON'T
LIKE THAT...STUFF!

03:37.002 --> 03:38.028
NOW, GIRLS, EAT
YOUR BROCCOLI.

03:39.000 --> 03:41.002
IT'S EXACTLY WHAT
GROWING SUPERHEROES
NEED

03:41.004 --> 03:42.019
TO CHARGE UP
THEIR POWERS.

03:42.021 --> 03:45.002
OH, IT'S PACKED WITH
ALL KINDS OF VITAMINS
AND MINERALS

03:45.004 --> 03:48.000
AND MMM-MMM!
IT'S SO GOOD FOR YOU!

03:48.002 --> 03:50.000
TOO BAD
IT TASTES
SO NASTY.

03:50.002 --> 03:51.018
YOU HAVEN'T EVEN
TASTED IT YET.

03:51.020 --> 03:52.021
SHH!

03:52.023 --> 03:53.023
WELL, YOU'RE NOT
LEAVING THE TABLE

03:53.025 --> 03:55.008
UNTIL YOUR BROCCOLI
IS ALL GONE.

03:55.010 --> 03:57.005
AND THE ONLY WAY TO
GET RID OF BROCCOLI

03:57.007 --> 03:59.018
IS TO EAT IT ALL UP
LIKE THIS!

03:59.020 --> 04:02.003
EEW!
ICK!
NO!

04:03.009 --> 04:04.024
Alien:
YOUR HIGHNESS,

04:04.026 --> 04:08.003
READINGS SHOW
THE RECEPTOR SPORES
HAVE BEEN INGESTED.

04:08.005 --> 04:10.009
EXCELLENT.

04:10.020 --> 04:15.000
THE TIME IS RIPE
TO INITIATE
HYPNOTRANSMYTHESIS.

04:15.002 --> 04:17.026
NOW THE EARTH'S
BARBARIC MAMMAL PEOPLE

04:17.028 --> 04:21.000
SHALL BE HYPNOTIZED
INTO A VEGETABLE STATE,

04:21.002 --> 04:22.013
ALLOWING MY WARRIORS

04:22.015 --> 04:25.019
TO REAP THROUGH
THE EARTH'S
ANIMAL POPULATION

04:25.021 --> 04:28.017
AND WEED OUT ALL
THE HUMAN BEINGS,

04:28.019 --> 04:31.005
LEAVING WE,
THE BROCCOLOID EMPIRE,

04:31.007 --> 04:33.021
TO HARVEST THE FRUITS
OF THE EARTH

04:33.023 --> 04:38.001
AND PLANT THE SEEDS
OF A NEW EMPIRE!

04:38.003 --> 04:40.015
[LAUGHS EVILLY]

04:40.017 --> 04:42.014
PROFESSOR? PROFESSOR?

04:42.016 --> 04:43.018
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

04:43.020 --> 04:46.010
YOU SEE, I TOLD
YOU THAT STUFF
WAS WRONG.

04:46.012 --> 04:48.025
WHY DID YOU EAT IT,
PROFESSOR? WHY?

04:48.027 --> 04:54.010
Narrator: JUST THEN, THE GIRLS'
ULTRASONIC HEARING IS BOMBARDED
WITH CRIES FOR HELP.

04:54.012 --> 04:57.012
SOUNDS LIKE WE'RE
NOT THE ONLY ONES
IN TROUBLE.

04:57.014 --> 04:58.023
WE GOTTA FIND OUT
WHAT'S GOING ON!

04:58.025 --> 05:00.026
Narrator: SO THE GIRLS
HEAD OUT ACROSS TOWNSVILLE,

05:00.028 --> 05:03.016
BUT EVERYWHERE THEY GO,
THE STORY'S THE SAME--

05:03.018 --> 05:05.012
MY MOM WAS TRYING
TO MAKE US
EAT BROCCOLI,

05:05.014 --> 05:07.014
BUT I WOULDN'T,
SO SHE ATE IT,
AND HER--

05:07.016 --> 05:11.007
EYES STARTED GLOWIN',
AND THEN THEY JUST
ZONKED OUT, MAN!

05:11.009 --> 05:14.000
JUST LIKE
THE PROFESSOR!

05:14.002 --> 05:16.009
WE'VE GOT TO INVESTIGATE
THAT BROCCOLI!

05:16.011 --> 05:19.011
Narrator: SO THE GIRLS TRACED
THE BROCCOLI BACK TO ITS ROOTS

05:19.013 --> 05:22.012
IN HOPES OF UNEARTHING
SOME CLUES.

05:23.025 --> 05:26.008
Bubbles:
HEY, GIRLS!
OVER HERE!

05:26.010 --> 05:28.000
WHAT IS IT?

05:28.002 --> 05:29.016
LOOKS LIKE
A MISSILE.

05:29.018 --> 05:31.003
OR A WEIRD
PEA POD.

05:31.005 --> 05:32.006
OR BOTH!

05:32.008 --> 05:33.009
Narrator:
UPON CLOSER INSPECTION,

05:33.011 --> 05:35.003
BLOSSOM'S MICROSCOPIC VISION
REVEALS--

05:35.005 --> 05:40.006
Blossom:
IT WAS CARRYING SOME SORT OF
ALIEN MIND CONTROL SPORES.

05:40.008 --> 05:42.011
THERE'S SPORES ALL OVER
THIS FIELD.

05:42.013 --> 05:44.009
IT MUST HAVE INFECTED
THE BROCCOLI.

05:44.011 --> 05:46.021
BUT WHY?
WHERE DID IT
COME FROM?

05:46.023 --> 05:49.012
Buttercup:
LOOKS LIKE WE'RE ABOUT
TO GET OUR ANSWER.

05:49.014 --> 05:51.006
Blossom:
QUICK, HIDE!

05:55.002 --> 06:00.023
LEAFTENANT, BRANCH OUT
AND SCOUT THE AREA FOR
OUR FIRST WAVE OF INVASION.

06:00.025 --> 06:01.015
WHAT?

06:01.017 --> 06:02.028
NOBODY INVADES
EARTH!

06:03.000 --> 06:03.027
WITHOUT A FIGHT!

06:03.029 --> 06:07.013
FROM THE POWERPUFF GIRLS!

06:08.005 --> 06:09.002
EARTH CREATURES!

06:09.004 --> 06:10.015
WHY AREN'T YOU
HYPNOTIZED?

06:10.017 --> 06:14.010
'CAUSE WE DIDN'T EAT NONE OF
YOUR DIABOLOGICAL SPORES.

06:14.012 --> 06:16.026
WELL, THEN, EAT THIS!

06:36.021 --> 06:37.021
AAH!

06:37.023 --> 06:39.018
THAT SCARED
THE PANTS
OFF OF ME!

06:39.020 --> 06:41.026
HOW ARE WE EVER
GONNA STOP 'EM?

06:41.028 --> 06:44.020
THE ONLY WAY
TO GET RID OF
YOUR BROCCOLI

06:44.022 --> 06:48.027
IS TO EAT IT
ALL UP.

06:57.020 --> 06:59.000
BARBARIANS!

06:59.002 --> 07:00.016
EEW! EEW! EEW!

07:00.018 --> 07:02.011
UGH! NASTY!

07:02.013 --> 07:03.019
SWALLOW YOUR
PRIDE, GIRLS!

07:03.021 --> 07:06.017
WE GOTTA EAT 'EM
TO BEAT 'EM.

07:16.020 --> 07:18.020
I'M GETTING FULL!

07:18.022 --> 07:21.014
I THINK I'VE
GOT ROOM FOR
ONE MORE!

07:21.016 --> 07:24.016
WHAT? YOU'RE GETTING
FULL ALREADY?

07:24.018 --> 07:27.011
BUT THAT WAS JUST
AN APPETIZER.

07:27.013 --> 07:31.001
HERE COMES
THE MAIN COURSE!

07:31.003 --> 07:33.003
UH-OH, WE'RE
GONNA NEED
SOME HELP!

07:33.005 --> 07:38.007
WHAT'S THE MATTER,
DON'T HAVE THE STOMACH FOR IT?

07:38.009 --> 07:41.005
Narrator:
AND WITH THAT, THE GIRLS
RETREAT BACK TO TOWNSVILLE

07:41.007 --> 07:43.002
TO ENLIST THE AID OF
THE OTHER CHILDREN.

07:43.004 --> 07:46.003
SO YOU SEE,
THE ONLY WAY TO
SAVE THE EARTH

07:46.005 --> 07:47.025
IS BY EATING
BROCCOLI.

07:47.027 --> 07:49.012
OH, DON'T
BELIEVE HER.

07:49.014 --> 07:51.004
THIS IS JUST
SOME KIND OF
TRICK

07:51.006 --> 07:52.018
TO GET US TO EAT
VEGETABLES.

07:52.020 --> 07:54.027
WHAT? YOU DOUBT
THE WORD OF
A POWERPUFF?

07:54.029 --> 07:57.013
OR MAYBE YOU'RE
JUST SCARED TO
EAT VEGETABLES?

07:57.015 --> 07:58.024
TELL YOU WHAT.

07:58.026 --> 08:00.007
WHY DON'T YOU
JUST RUN ON HOME
TO YOUR MAMA

08:00.009 --> 08:02.023
AND SEE IF
SHE'LL MAKE YOU
A BOLOGNA SANDWICH.

08:02.025 --> 08:05.005
OH, WAIT.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

08:05.007 --> 08:06.018
SHE CAN'T,

08:06.020 --> 08:08.018
'CAUSE SHE'S
BEEN ZAPNOTIZED
BY ALIEN INVADERS!

08:08.020 --> 08:10.009
BUT YOU DON'T WANT
TO HELP SAVE HER

08:10.011 --> 08:15.002
'CAUSE YOU DON'T
FEEL LIKE EATING
A FEW VEGETABLES!

08:16.012 --> 08:19.029
LET'S DO IT FOR THE FOLKS!

08:20.014 --> 08:23.022
[CHEERING]

08:23.024 --> 08:25.019
LET ME AT 'EM!
LET ME AT 'EM!

08:25.021 --> 08:30.005
Narrator: AND SO,
AS THE VEGETARIAN FORCES
MOBILIZE FOR INVASION,

08:30.007 --> 08:34.019
THE CHILDREN OF TOWNSVILLE
GIRD THEIR LOINS FOR BATTLE.

08:34.021 --> 08:36.015
[SIREN WAILS]

08:51.015 --> 08:52.021
HALT!

08:52.023 --> 08:56.003
COLONEL, LET'S TRIM BACK
THAT OVERGROWN CITY.

08:56.005 --> 08:59.002
ARTILLERY,
ON MY MARK.

08:59.004 --> 09:00.005
READY,

09:00.007 --> 09:01.019
AIM,

09:01.021 --> 09:02.029
FIRE!

09:06.026 --> 09:11.018
THOSE LITTLE SPROUTS
HAVE PUMPED MY
TANKS!

09:11.020 --> 09:12.015
NO MATTER.

09:12.017 --> 09:14.012
INFANTRY,
AFTER THEM!

09:14.014 --> 09:16.009
STORM THE CITY!

09:20.006 --> 09:22.024
RELEASE THE CHEESE!

09:24.023 --> 09:31.019
HUH? NO!

09:31.021 --> 09:33.015
CHARGE!

09:33.017 --> 09:36.005
[CHEERING]

09:37.004 --> 09:39.022
[CHEERING]

09:54.006 --> 09:54.023
82.

09:54.025 --> 09:55.016
36.

09:55.018 --> 09:57.005
BITE!

10:07.024 --> 10:09.006
OW!

10:09.008 --> 10:11.028
[LAUGHS EVILLY]

10:13.022 --> 10:16.014
47 STALKS.

10:16.016 --> 10:21.005
THE HORROR,
THE HORROR.

10:21.007 --> 10:22.004
STAY DOWN, SOLDIER.

10:22.006 --> 10:24.016
YOU'VE SEEN
ENOUGH ACTION.

10:24.018 --> 10:27.005
BLOSSOM, A LOT OF US
ARE GETTING REALLY FULL.

10:27.007 --> 10:29.021
I DON'T KNOW
HOW MUCH MORE WE CAN EAT.

10:29.023 --> 10:31.018
SIRE, THEIR FORCES
ARE WEAKENING.

10:31.020 --> 10:33.009
WE HAVE THEM
ON THE RUN.

10:33.011 --> 10:34.014
EXCELLENT.

10:34.016 --> 10:38.003
IT'S ONLY
A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE--WHAT?

10:43.019 --> 10:47.025
Narrator: OHO! HERE COMES
THE HUNGRY CAVALRY!

10:58.010 --> 11:00.009
HOORAY!

11:00.011 --> 11:02.014
CHARGE!

11:02.016 --> 11:05.000
RETREAT!

11:10.000 --> 11:11.019
WHOA!

11:12.021 --> 11:15.005
[CHEERING]

11:15.007 --> 11:18.000
NO! NO! LEAF ME ALONE!

11:18.002 --> 11:21.007
I DON'T DESERVE THIS!

11:27.006 --> 11:30.024
[CHEERING]

11:32.026 --> 11:34.026
Narrator: SO, WITH
THE BROCCOLOIDS DEVOURED

11:34.028 --> 11:36.029
AND THE HYPNOTRASNMYTHESIZER
DESTROYED,

11:37.001 --> 11:38.013
THE PARENTS OF TOWNSVILLE
AWAKEN,

11:38.015 --> 11:43.028
AND FAMILIES ONCE TORN APART
BY WAR ARE REUNITED ONCE AGAIN.

11:44.000 --> 11:45.017
AND AS NORMAL LIFE RESUMES,

11:45.019 --> 11:47.006
WE JOIN
THE UTONIUM FAMILY

11:47.008 --> 11:49.003
ON AN OUTING TO
THE SUPERMARKET.

11:49.005 --> 11:51.004
WHY DON'T YOU GIRLS GO
PICK OUT SOME CEREAL

11:51.006 --> 11:53.003
AND I'LL MEET YOU
IN THE PRODUCE AISLE?

11:53.005 --> 11:54.011
OK!

11:54.013 --> 11:57.011
WE'LL SEE IF WE CAN'T FIND
SOME GREENS THEY WILL EAT.

11:57.013 --> 11:58.008
[GROWLS AND SHOUTS]

11:58.010 --> 11:59.009
GIVE 'EM HECK,
TROOPS!

11:59.011 --> 12:01.010
WE'LL SHOW 'EM
WHO'S BOSS!

12:01.012 --> 12:04.016
YOU CAN NEVER BE
TOO CAREFUL!

12:07.027 --> 12:11.024
AND SO, ONCE AGAIN,
THE DAY IS SAVED

12:11.026 --> 12:14.010
THANKS TO THE POWERPUFF GIRLS!

12:14.012 --> 12:18.017
AND THE HUNGRY LITTLE TYKES
OF TOWNSVILLE.

12:31.016 --> 12:33.029
THE CITY OF TOWNSVILLE.

12:34.001 --> 12:35.023
A TIDY TOWN,

12:35.025 --> 12:41.019
WHERE THE TOWNSVILLE TOWNIES
TAKE PRIDE IN KEEPING
THEIR TINY TOWN TIDY.

12:45.010 --> 12:46.029
[EXPLOSION]

12:58.025 --> 13:01.001
[LAUGHS]

13:28.010 --> 13:29.024
WHAT A MESS!

13:29.026 --> 13:32.006
WELL, GUESS OUR WORK'S
DONE HERE!

13:32.008 --> 13:33.011
COME ON!

13:33.013 --> 13:35.025
OH, I FEEL
SO DIRTY.

13:35.027 --> 13:39.018
I KNOW.
ISN'T IT GREAT?

13:40.011 --> 13:42.000
Dr. Utonium:
WELCOME HOME, GIRLS.

13:42.002 --> 13:44.024
I RAN A NICE,
HOT BATH FOR YOU.

13:44.026 --> 13:46.011
A BATH!
A BATH!

13:46.013 --> 13:48.016
A BATH?

13:53.021 --> 13:56.009
[GIGGLING]

13:56.011 --> 13:58.017
COME ON IN,
BUTTERCUP!

13:58.019 --> 14:01.016
THE WATER'S FINE!

14:02.026 --> 14:07.026
DON'T YOU KNOW THAT ONLY
BIG FAT SISSIES TAKE BATHS?

14:07.028 --> 14:10.006
I'M NOT FAT.

14:11.005 --> 14:13.005
[ROARS]

14:18.005 --> 14:21.000
BLECH! THIS IS
GONNA GET NASTY!

14:21.002 --> 14:23.010
IT SURE IS!

14:28.012 --> 14:29.026
HEY!

14:33.029 --> 14:35.018
EEW.
EEW.

14:49.020 --> 14:51.026
[ROARS]

15:02.000 --> 15:04.011
AND STAY DOWN,
SUCKER!

15:04.013 --> 15:06.000
LET'S GO!

15:11.011 --> 15:15.012
IS IT ME, OR DOES
BUTTERCUP STINK?

15:23.026 --> 15:26.012
[ROARS]

15:27.020 --> 15:29.012
[GIGGLING]

15:33.007 --> 15:34.018
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

15:34.020 --> 15:38.000
DON'T YOU KNOW YOU'RE JUST GONNA
GET DIRTY AGAIN TOMORROW?

15:38.002 --> 15:39.023
SHEESH.

15:45.009 --> 15:46.007
[SNIFFS]

15:46.009 --> 15:48.004
[GLASS BREAKS]

15:48.006 --> 15:50.005
BUTTERCUP, YOU STINK.
TAKE A BATH.

15:50.007 --> 15:54.027
ARGH. WHAT'S THE SUDDEN INTEREST
IN MY PERSONAL HYGIENE?

15:54.029 --> 15:56.020
I'M NOT TAKING A BATH!

15:56.022 --> 15:58.009
AND IF YOU DON'T LIKE IT,

15:58.011 --> 15:59.019
THROW ME OUT!

15:59.021 --> 16:00.015
[DOOR SLAMS]

16:00.017 --> 16:03.003
FINE. WHO NEEDS YOU?

16:04.011 --> 16:05.027
[ROOSTER CROWS]

16:05.029 --> 16:10.021
I JUST HOPE BUTTERCUP
REMEMBERS TO GET
TO SCHOOL ON TIME.

16:15.003 --> 16:17.026
[ROAR]

16:36.013 --> 16:37.022
[CRASH]

16:40.019 --> 16:43.020
HA HA!
HA HA!

17:00.001 --> 17:01.016
[ROARS]

17:12.019 --> 17:16.010
HA HA!

17:18.029 --> 17:21.015
NOW, GRAPES ARE GREEN,

17:21.017 --> 17:23.005
AND WHAT ELSE IS GREEN?

17:23.007 --> 17:25.010
GRASS, THAT'S RIGHT!

17:25.012 --> 17:27.013
NOW, AN APPLE IS RED.

17:27.015 --> 17:29.027
WHO CAN TELL ME
WHAT ELSE IS RED--

17:29.029 --> 17:31.000
[SNIFFS]

17:31.002 --> 17:32.015
EEW!

17:37.025 --> 17:39.010
SORRY I'M LATE,
MISS K.

17:39.012 --> 17:42.020
I WAS JUST STOPPING
AN EVIL MONSTER.

17:42.026 --> 17:44.000
[ALARM SOUNDS]

17:44.002 --> 17:45.006
WELL, WHAT DO YOU KNOW, KIDS.
A FIRE DRILL.

17:45.008 --> 17:47.006
I GUESS WE ALL BETTER
GET OUT OF HERE.

17:47.008 --> 17:48.009
[CHEERS]

17:48.011 --> 17:51.028
[NASALLY]
BUTTERCUP, YOU STAY.

17:52.028 --> 17:56.005
AH, WHO NEEDS 'EM.

18:16.028 --> 18:19.006
[COUGH]

18:19.008 --> 18:22.003
[TELEPHONES RINGING]

18:22.005 --> 18:25.009
YES, YES, I KNOW!
I SMELL IT, TOO!

18:25.011 --> 18:29.019
DO YOU THINK I'M BLIND?
OF COURSE I SMELL IT!

18:29.021 --> 18:34.009
YES, YES, UH-HUH.
I KNOW, YES.

18:34.011 --> 18:37.024
SOMETHING MUST BE DONE!

18:41.004 --> 18:43.017
HEY, WHERE DID EVERYBODY GO?

18:43.019 --> 18:45.025
Man: THERE SHE IS!

18:47.013 --> 18:50.000
[SHOUTING]

18:51.000 --> 18:51.028
BUTTERCUP!

18:52.000 --> 18:53.026
THANK GOODNESS
WE FOUND YOU.

18:53.028 --> 18:55.011
AS MAYOR OF
TOWNSVILLE,

18:55.013 --> 18:59.012
I FEEL IT IS
MY SWORN DUTY
TO TELL YOU THAT

18:59.014 --> 19:00.024
YOU STINK!

19:00.026 --> 19:01.022
YOU SMELL!

19:01.024 --> 19:02.025
YOU REEK!

19:02.027 --> 19:05.022
YOU'RE STINKING UP
THE WHOLE TOWN.

19:05.024 --> 19:07.015
SO EITHER
TAKE A BATH

19:07.017 --> 19:09.001
OR TAKE A HIKE!

19:09.003 --> 19:10.008
ENOUGH TALK!

19:10.010 --> 19:12.003
IT'S BURN TIME!

19:12.005 --> 19:14.026
[CROWD SHOUTS AGREEMENT]

19:26.020 --> 19:28.021
[BARKING DOGS]

19:32.002 --> 19:34.006
WAIT! WHAT AM I DOING?

19:34.008 --> 19:37.006
WHERE'D SHE GO?

19:45.014 --> 19:47.015
HMM. FIRST MY FAMILY,

19:47.017 --> 19:48.017
THEN MY FRIENDS,

19:48.019 --> 19:50.011
AND NOW TOWNSVILLE.

19:50.013 --> 19:55.013
I MEAN, WHAT DOES BEING CLEAN
HAVE TO DO WITH BEING
A SUPERHERO, ANYWAY?

19:55.015 --> 19:56.020
WHO NEEDS THEM?

19:56.022 --> 19:59.007
AS LONG AS I CAN FIGHT
MONSTERS AND STUFF,

19:59.009 --> 20:01.025
I AIN'T NEVER COMING CLEAN!

20:13.000 --> 20:17.007
[GROWL]

20:18.009 --> 20:22.002
NOW, THAT'S WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT!

20:26.001 --> 20:31.004
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO DO
BETTER THAN THAT!

20:39.017 --> 20:44.000
YEOW! GET IT OUT, GET IT OUT!

20:51.002 --> 20:52.008
HEY, WAIT!

20:52.010 --> 20:53.014
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

20:53.016 --> 20:56.015
UH, I WAS GONNA
GO HOME.

20:56.017 --> 20:57.006
WHY?

20:57.008 --> 20:58.008
OH, I DON'T KNOW.

20:58.010 --> 21:01.007
MAYBE BECAUSE...
YOU STINK!

21:01.009 --> 21:02.023
WHAT?!

21:02.025 --> 21:06.024
[STAMMERING]

21:07.003 --> 21:09.012
ALL RIGHT, I'LL DO IT!

21:09.014 --> 21:11.012
I'LL TAKE THAT STUPID--

21:11.014 --> 21:14.011
BATH.

21:38.001 --> 21:39.025
NOW, THEN.
SEE, BUTTERCUP?

21:39.027 --> 21:43.022
DON'T YOU FEEL BETTER
NOW THAT YOU'RE ALL
SQUEAKY CLEAN?

21:43.024 --> 21:46.011
"NOW THAT YOU'RE ALL
SQUEAKY CLEAN..."

21:46.013 --> 21:47.011
SHUT UP!

21:47.013 --> 21:49.007
I ONLY TOOK
THIS STUPID BATH

21:49.009 --> 21:51.022
SO I COULD FIGHT
MONSTERS AGAIN.

21:51.024 --> 21:52.021
YOU KNOW, BUTTERCUP,

21:52.023 --> 21:53.023
YOU MAY BE CLEAN,

21:53.025 --> 21:55.029
BUT YOUR ATTITUDE
STILL STINKS.

21:56.001 --> 21:57.025
Narrator:
RIPE YOU ARE, BUTTERCUP,

21:57.027 --> 22:00.008
I MEAN, RIGHT YOU ARE, BLOSSOM.

22:00.010 --> 22:07.006
